text: Vyllelm king gret Hereman biscop, & Wulstan biscop, & Eustace eorl, & Eadrich, & Bristrich, & ealle mine þegenes on Wyltoneshyre & on Glouceastershyre fronliche.
& ic cuþe eow ic habbe geunnan Reinbold mina preost þæt land æt Esi, & þæt land æt Latton, & ealle þæra þinge þæt þar to lið binnan port & buten.
Mið sace & mið socne swa full and swa forð, swa his furmest on hondan stodan Harald kinge, on ællan þingan, on dæge & æfter, to atheonne, swa swa ealra lefest ys.
& ic nelle nenna men geþafian þæt him fram honda teo ænig þære þinga þæs þa ic him geunne habbe bi minan freonshype.
